schemaVersion: 1
id: newborn-root
name: Newborn (0–3 months)
kind: root
version: 0.1.0
description: >
  The survival cabinet for weeks 0–12 with a brand-new baby. Pairs with
  mom-command (the always-installed root). One agent: Martha, your newborn
  counselor — same Martha as every other Mom & Baby cabinet, just titled for
  this stage. Full-screen Survival Tracker webapp, 20 short wiki pages on
  newborn essentials, milestone CSV, and a clear red-flags page for when to
  call the doctor.
entry: index.md
